{"tid":569570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近食咗條女","createTime":"2018-02-22T21:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T11:28:12.000Z","uid":171555,"like":333,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"74d96101fe521a783d4ce0dc4494eb5f978f5f05","tid":569570,"uid":171555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T21:12:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好食懶既女人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說 是咁的<br />\n約咗條女 之前見過一次 今次就再出<br />\n上次見佢 佢話化左 但我睇同無化一樣 今次都係<br />\n咁化唔化妝對我無乜所謂<br />\n食完飯 行咗陣 就開房啦<br />\n錫下 攬下 渣下波咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就叫佢一齊去沖涼<br />\n佢話 可唔可以唔沖 懶<br />\n心諗 ok fine 我一陣扑完自己沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁繼續 除左佢衫 跌左對D cup 波出黎 手感幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後除左條底 一睇 嘩 屌你老母 唔講以為去左亞馬遜森林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要同我講未剪過 <br />\n唉 算 熄左燈都一樣既姐<br />\n玩到咁上下咪男上入囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攬住佢搞個陣 索到佢d頭髮 雖然唔係好撚臭 都好影響心情<br />\n轉個狗仔式諗住好d 嘩屌 個臭閪陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻勇上黎 乜心情都無哂"},{"pid":"26ccf0c524b21ba1abc8ee06404101cce34a37c7","tid":569570,"uid":172618,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T21:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01d2256ba19c2bbcab4e48c1fc2a6fa34377f66","tid":569570,"uid":171555,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"26ccf0c524b21ba1abc8ee06404101cce34a37c7","tid":569570,"uid":172618,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T21:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/